==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Buzzer
<hw>Buzz"er</hw> <pr>(b⟦ucr⟧z"⟦etil⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who,
or that which, buzzes; a whisperer; a talebearer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And wants not <qex>buzzers</qex> to infect his ear⟦br⟧
With pestilent speeches of his father's death.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Buzzingly</ent>⟦br⟧
